OL,6,FMel Barham reports on the sentencing
OL,7,Fof Ashley Darbyshire at Liverpool
OL,8,FCrown Court
OL,10,FA man with a "crazed attitude to sex"
OL,11,Fgroomed a schoolgirl and then enjoyed
OL,12,Fwatching others further degrade her in
OL,13,Fa "den of iniquity", a judge has said.
OL,15,FAshley Darbyshire, 28, targeted his
OL,16,Fvictim from the age of 13 with
OL,17,Fsexualised messages on Facebook and
OL,18,Frepeated demands to meet her in person.
