OL,7,FApril to 15 years in jail, Judge Simon
OL,8,FMedland KC told him: "You cajoled and
OL,9,Fthreatened her and pretended to have
OL,10,Faffection for her.
OL,12,F"She was simply a simply object to
OL,13,Fyou, a human sexual commodity which
OL,14,Fyou consumed as and when you wished.
OL,16,F"Your treatment of her was coldly
OL,17,Fsexualised and you manipulated her in
OL,18,Fyour ways.
