OL,6,F"You had a crazed attitude to sex
OL,7,Fwhich in the main was an exercise of
OL,8,Fpower and control."
OL,10,FThe court heard that Derbyshire, who
OL,11,Fgroomed his victim from when he was
OL,12,Faged 19, had a "long history" of
OL,13,Fsexualised conduct with teenage girls
OL,14,Fwho he also contacted online.
OL,16,FLast month he also admitted committing
OL,17,Fsexual offences against four other
OL,18,Fcomplainants including the rape of a
OL,19,Fgirl aged 15.
