OL,6,FHe was due to go on trial last year
OL,7,Fwith his co-defendants but had a brain
OL,8,Fhaemorrhage in August.
OL,10,FDue to his condition Darbyshire, of
OL,11,FWesthoughton, Bolton, was now unable
OL,12,Fto recall his offending, the court was
OL,13,Ftold.
OL,15,FIn February eight other men were
OL,16,Fconvicted at Liverpool Crown Court of
OL,17,Fvarious sexual offences against the
OL,18,Fcomplainant who was groomed from the
OL,19,Fage of 13.
