OL,6,FAlso sentenced on Monday was Brandon
OL,7,FHarwood, 25, from Bolton, who was
OL,8,Fjailed for 10 years for offences of
OL,9,Frape, attempted rape and sexual
OL,10,Factivity with a child.
OL,12,FRoss Corley, 30, of Bolton, pleaded
OL,13,Fguilty at an earlier hearing to two
OL,14,Fcounts of sexual activity with a child
OL,15,Fand was jailed for 28 months.
OL,17,FHarvie Aspden, 25, of Bury, received a
OL,18,F15-month jail term, suspended for two
OL,19,Fyears, after he was convicted of
OL,20,Fsexual activity with the complainant
OL,21,Fwhen he was 17 and she was aged 14.
