OL,11,F"I'd rather be dead most days than
OL,12,Fdeal with all this mental torture and
OL,13,Fmemories.
OL,15,F"I shouldn't have had to grow up so
OL,16,Fyoung and spend the rest of my life
OL,17,F'healing' from what these monsters did
OL,18,Fto me, leaving me in my own prison I
OL,19,Fbuilt for myself in my own mind for
OL,20,Fthe rest of my life.
